## Introduction

The SCM app allows importing and managing a forecast using PowerPredictive. Additionally, it enables the calculation and optimization of certain planning parameters. Below is a list of implemented features:

<table>
	<tr>
		<td>1</td>
		<td>Data export for PowerPredictive via API</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>2</td>
		<td>Forecast import from PowerPredictive</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>3</td>
		<td>Calculation of item status and forecast using formulas</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>4</td>
		<td>Update of reorder point and safety stock:
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>



